OL,3,CBergerac reboot 'a love letter to the
OL,4,Coriginal series'
OL,6,FA TV critic has praised the producers
OL,7,Fbehind the new Bergerac show, calling
OL,8,Fit "a love letter to the original
OL,9,Fseries".
OL,11,FScott Bryan believes they have struck
OL,12,Fthe right balance between reimagining
OL,13,Fthe 1980s drama for a modern audience
OL,14,Fand keeping some key elements that
OL,15,Ffans know and love.
OL,17,FHe explains: "Jersey remains a central
OL,18,Fcharacter in this and I think it's
OL,19,Fevident they've spent a lot of effort
OL,20,Freally trying to bring through the
OL,21,Fcharm and sites.
