OL,3,CBergerac reboot 'a love letter to the
OL,4,Coriginal series'
OL,6,F"It retains quite a lot of the
OL,7,Ffeatures that made it such a massive
OL,8,Fhit. It's also tried to maybe move on
OL,9,Fwith the times and reflect something
OL,10,Fmore current.
OL,12,F"A big difference viewers will notice
OL,13,Fis it manages to have one self-
OL,14,Fcontained story over the whole series
OL,15,Frather than episodes that end up being
OL,16,Fentirely different."
