OL,3,CBergerac reboot 'a love letter to the
OL,4,Coriginal series'
OL,6,FThe iconic title detective is played
OL,7,Fby Damien Molony as he succeeds John
OL,8,FNettles and this series shows Bergerac
OL,9,Fbattling his own struggles while
OL,10,Ftrying to solve a murder case.
OL,12,FScott adds: "Bergerac is a similar
OL,13,Fcharacter to the 1980s but at the same
OL,14,Ftime, they've tried to bring in more
OL,15,Fmodern aspects.
