OL,3,CBergerac reboot 'a love letter to the
OL,4,Coriginal series'
OL,6,F"For example, he is trying to recover
OL,7,Ffrom his addiction to alcohol so now
OL,8,Fhe's in an AA (Alcohols Anonymous)
OL,9,Fmeeting. There's a lot of talk about
OL,10,Fmen's mental health, trying to seek
OL,11,Ftherapy and his attitude towards it."
OL,13,FScott believes while the series may
OL,14,Fecho other dramas, its heritage could
OL,15,Fhelp it stand out in a crowded market.
