OL,3,CBergerac reboot 'a love letter to the
OL,4,Coriginal series'
OL,6,FHe says: "It's quite similar to other
OL,7,Fcrime shows that are on TV now but I
OL,8,Fthink Bergerac has the potential to do
OL,9,Fvery well because it is a reboot of a
OL,10,Fmuch-loved series and I think it also
OL,11,Fmanages to retain a lot of the charm
OL,12,Fthat made the original series popular.
OL,14,F"Crime dramas are a very popular
OL,15,Fformat on British TV, it's also one of
OL,16,Four greatest exports and I think
OL,17,FBergerac was one of the series that
OL,18,Fcatapulted this form into mainstream
OL,19,FTV.
