OL,3,CBergerac reboot 'a love letter to the
OL,4,Coriginal series'
OL,6,F"Good, strong performances by the
OL,7,Fcentral lead characters, an
OL,8,Finteresting central hook and without
OL,9,Fgiving away spoilers, the interplay
OL,10,Fbetween the investigation and where it
OL,11,Fleads is a bit original compared to a
OL,12,Flot of typical crime thrillers.
OL,14,F"The fact it's managed to attract the
OL,15,Flikes of Zoe Wanamaker, Philip
OL,16,FGlenister, Damien Molony, these are
OL,17,Fhousehold names that people will
OL,18,Frecognise and they bring a lot of
OL,19,Fcharacter to their roles.
