OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F382A1740705674
OL,3,CBergerac reboot 'a love letter to the
OL,4,Coriginal series'
OL,6,F"The one thing that comes through from
OL,7,Fwatching this is how much love there
OL,8,Fis for the original series. This
OL,9,Fdoesn't feel like a reboot that's been
OL,10,Fknocked together quickly.
OL,12,F"Jersey is such a central character in
OL,13,Fthis, I mean it's hard for it not to
OL,14,Fbe. It really shines through and I
OL,15,Fthink it will be a massive boost to
OL,16,Ftourism when this series debuts,
OL,17,Fhopefully as much impact as the
OL,18,Foriginal series had back in the 80s.
