OL,3,CBergerac reboot 'a love letter to the
OL,4,Coriginal series'
OL,6,F"A particular joy in the original, you
OL,7,Fwould always end up having car chases
OL,8,Fon the same roads because there's only
OL,9,Fso many in Jersey. You wonder as a
OL,10,Fviewer whether that's going to happen
OL,11,Fagain."
OL,13,FThe full Bergerac series is available
OL,14,Fto watch in the British Isles on the
OL,15,Ffree streaming platform U.
OL,17,FIt will also be shown on the free-to-
OL,18,Fair TV channel U&Drama every Thursday
OL,19,Fat 9pm and has been sold to several
OL,20,Finternational broadcasters.
